Attractive and designed to go with you everywhere, the iPod touch is available in 5 stunning colors to suit anyone's taste.</p>

items.name: Plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset
items.shortDescription: The Plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset is so lightweight and comfortable that you may forget you're wearing it. During setup, you simply follow the voice prompts to select English, Spanish or French for the audible status alerts on talk time, battery level, connection and more. You can also control music tracks and volume without touching your smartphone. If you forget the Bluetooth headset for smartphone in the car or at the office, the M70 knows to enter its DeepSleep hibernation mode to conserve the battery. Using it is so easy that you can finally free your cheek from your smartphone. It reduces wind and noise for a clear and crisp quality call and it makes for a comfortable fit with the three optional ear tips to choose from. <br>
items.longDescription: The Plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset allows you to do more with your voice and answer calls without even pressing a button and you can manage emails and much more.
